season\n | competition        = U18 Professional Development League\n | image              = \n | pixels             = \n | season             = 2016\u201317\n | winners            = \n | league topscorer   = \n | biggest home win   = \n | biggest away win   = \n | highest scoring    = \n | matches            = \n | total goals        = \n | longest wins       = \n | longest unbeaten   = \n | longest losses     = \n | highest attendance = \n | lowest attendance  = \n | prevseason         = [[2015\u201316 Professional U18 Development League#League 2|2015\u201316]]\n | nextseason         = [[2017\u201318 Professional Development League (Category 2)#U18 level|2017\u201318]]\n}}\nThe '''Professional U18 Development League 2''', also known as '''U18 PDL-2''', was split into two regional divisions.\n\nTeams played each team in their own division twice, and each team in the other division once, for a total of 28 games each.\n\nAt the end of the season, the teams finishing in the top two positions of both divisions met in the knockout stage to determine the overall league champion.\n\n===Tables===\n====North Division====\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n\n|team1=SHU|name_SHU=[[Sheffield United F.C. Academy|Sheffield United U18s]]\n|team2=SHW|name_SHW=[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C. Academy|Sheffield Wednesday U18s]]\n|team3=NOT|name_NOT=[[Nottingham Forest F.C. Under-21's Squad and Academy|Nottingham Forest U18s]]\n|team4=BOL|name_BOL=[[Bolton Wanderers F.C. Reserves and Academy#The Academy|Bolton Wanderers U18s]]\n|team5=HUD|name_HUD=[[Huddersfield Town F.C. Reserves and Academy|Huddersfield Town U18s]]\n|team6=CRE|name_CRE=[[Crewe Alexandra F.C. Academy|Crewe Alexandra U18s]]\n|team7=BAR|name_BAR=[[Barnsley F.C.|Barnsley U18s]]\n|team8=LEE|name_LEE=[[Leeds United A.F.C. Reserves and Youth Team|Leeds United U18s]]\n|team9=BIR|name_BIR=[[Birmingham City F.C. Reserves and Academy|Birmingham City U18s]]\n|team10=HUL|name_HUL=[[Hull City A.F.C. Reserves an